Test Script 5-6:  Perform Titer Acceptance Test

User clicks on Titer Cutpoint link and then adds a new dataset. Under that dataset, they will add 4 plates. Each plate will use the Titer Template. The data files for titer analysis are in the test script files\ADA\data\3. Titer Cutpoint folder. Name each plate in the order that it was added.  Each plate should be accepted after it is loaded and saved.
